And I think it might be helpful if there were a choice of, you know, a few different people, you know, cause we're already, you know, well, midstream into this, somebody who'd already had an interest in charter review, or maybe somebody like John and Mike and somebody who do this in their other life too, so that we don't have to, you know,

77
00:08:20,937 --> 00:08:25,220
We can bring them up to speed, but so that it doesn't have to be a, you know, let's start from step one.

78
