96
00:09:33,363 --> 00:09:36,325
And I don't know if we've actually thought of our mission statement.

97
00:09:36,345 --> 00:09:38,727
I know we've had a charge from the mayor of what we need to do.

98
00:09:40,379 --> 00:09:46,423
I really believe, and I'll share this, is that I think this charter process is a living document.

99
00:09:46,583 --> 00:09:50,606
It's not a let's pick three items out of it and let's move on.

100
00:09:51,206 --> 00:09:56,009
I think what we have to really establish, and hopefully with the help of the Collins Center, is a process.

101
00:09:56,818 --> 00:10:01,619
