147
00:14:04,409 --> 00:14:06,532
But that's part of the process.

148
00:14:07,792 --> 00:14:16,716
Um, I, one of the things I wanted to look at was just the, what I had written down in the notes was suggestions that we got from the people.

149
00:14:17,396 --> 00:14:20,877
So, and Ron, you brought up one of them, the qualifications.

150
00:14:21,097 --> 00:14:30,901
